OL,3,CReeves to go further with welfare cuts
OL,4,Cas she delivers her Spring Statement
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves is set to go
OL,7,Ffurther with cuts to welfare as she
OL,8,Fdelivers her Spring Statement on
OL,9,FWednesday.
OL,11,FThe Office for Budget Responsibility
OL,12,F(OBR) say the government's sums on
OL,13,Fbenefits cuts fall short of the #5bn
OL,14,Fthey said they'd save, meaning Reeves
OL,15,Fis now expected to announce a further
OL,16,F#500 million of savings through cuts
OL,17,Fto universal credit.
