OL,3,CReeves to go further with welfare cuts
OL,4,Cas she delivers her Spring Statement
OL,6,FA difficult economic climate, combined
OL,7,Fwith the fact that Reeves didn't leave
OL,8,Fherself much headroom in her Autumn
OL,9,FBudget, has left the chancellor in a
OL,10,Ftight spot. In order to honour a
OL,11,Fpledge not to break her self-imposed
OL,12,Ffiscal rules, she's set to find extra
OL,13,Fmoney through cuts.
OL,15,FThe speech is not a Budget, but has
OL,16,Fbecome a much more significant event
OL,17,Fthan the "update" it was initially
OL,18,Fbilled as by the Treasury.
