OL,3,CReeves to go further with welfare cuts
OL,4,Cas she delivers her Spring Statement
OL,6,FLast week the government announced
OL,7,Fhuge cuts to the benefits system,
OL,8,Fsaying they would save #5 billion by
OL,9,F2030.
OL,11,FBut now Reeves is expected to reveal
OL,12,Fthat the OBR has said that figure
OL,13,Fwould be much lower, so the government
OL,14,Fhas decided to announce a further #500
OL,15,Fmillion of savings.
