OL,3,CReeves to go further with welfare cuts
OL,4,Cas she delivers her Spring Statement
OL,6,FThe Chancellor is set to announce a
OL,7,Ffreeze of incapacity benefits for new
OL,8,Fclaimants until 2030, after an initial
OL,9,Fcut, and a reduction in the basic rate
OL,10,Fof universal credit in 2029, after an
OL,11,Fearlier increase.
OL,13,FAll eyes are also on the government's
OL,14,Fown impact assessment on how many
OL,15,Fpeople will be affected by the cuts,
OL,16,Fwith estimates suggesting one million
OL,17,Fdisabled people could be hit by the
OL,18,Fchanges to disability benefits.
