OL,4,Cas she delivers her Spring Statement
OL,6,FThe government say the plans are part
OL,7,Fof efforts to get people back to work,
OL,8,Fbut some backbench Labour MPs have
OL,9,Faccused Reeves using the cuts to
OL,10,F"balance the books on the backs of
OL,11,Fdisabled people".
OL,13,FWhile much of the focus will be on the
OL,14,Fcuts announced in Reeves' speech, what
OL,15,Fshe wants to highlight is the boost
OL,16,Fthe government is giving to defence
OL,17,Fspending.
