OL,3,CReeves to go further with welfare cuts
OL,4,Cas she delivers her Spring Statement
OL,6,FThe Treasury insists this increase
OL,7,Fwill not require additional borrowing
OL,8,Fand will "maintain the Chancellor's
OL,9,Fironclad fiscal rule". That's because
OL,10,Fsome of the spending is going on
OL,11,Fcapital projects, which aren't scored
OL,12,Fby the OBR.
OL,14,FReeves is set to blame the cuts she's
OL,15,Fmaking on "a world that is changing
OL,16,Fbefore our eyes", as Donald Trump's
OL,17,Finterventions in the Ukraine war have
OL,18,Fsparked concern about Europe's ability
OL,19,Fto defend itself without US support.
