OL,6,F"This moment demands an active
OL,7,Fgovernment stepping up to secure
OL,8,FBritain's future. A government on the
OL,9,Fside of working people."
OL,11,FCivil Service
OL,13,FAt the weekend, the chancellor
OL,14,Fannounced she will cut Civil Service
OL,15,Frunning costs by 15%, cutting jobs by
OL,16,F10,000.
OL,18,FThe move is expected to save #2.2
OL,19,Fbillion a year by 2029-30, scrapping
OL,20,Fsome jobs described by Reeves as "back
OL,21,Foffice", like communications and HR.
